accessibility.text: TOWNHOUSE is the collaborative magic of Paul Brown & Christoph Brooke. With over 40 years of industry experience between them, we believe we have a couple of chaps who will inspire our team of wild hearts and open minds to achieve a brand to be proud of.

Why are we so excited? Because we’ve done oodles of research and developed a concept, that frankly, takes the best bits from everyone else and adds a healthy dose of our own imagination. You’ll get Lux style and comfort for a midrange price and you’ll get sexy tech to not only check-in & out but control bits and bobs in your room and connect you directly to the neighbourhood on our doorstep.
Some of the key steps to our world domination
12 properties in UK regional cities in five years
A minimum of 80 bedrooms per property
6 times earnings on EBITDA by Year 6
with  a further investment opportunity in year 3
